    "movableInEdit": false,
    "css": "font-size: 23px; ",
    "text": "Three-dimensional dice ('shape3d':true) can be added from the Add Widget overlay. When adding a dice, you can pick the number of faces that are available. For the cube dice, you pick a color (default is white). When clicked, all but the cube animate by transforming (rolling or flipping) between several faces. The cube animates by shaking. If you pick more sides than are available in a shape, the dice will display the next smallest valid geometrical shape, but will still choose from any specified face when rolled."
  },
